member.name: CompositingQuality
member.summary: The CompositingQuality enumeration specifies whether gamma correction is applied when colors are blended with background colors. This enumeration is used by the and methods of theGraphics class.

member.name: CompositingQuality.CompositingQualityDefault
member.summary: Specifies that gamma correction is not applied.

member.name: CompositingQuality.CompositingQualityHighSpeed
member.summary: Specifies that gamma correction is not applied.

member.name: CompositingQuality.CompositingQualityHighQuality
member.summary: Specifies that gamma correction is applied.

member.name: CompositingQuality.CompositingQualityGammaCorrected
member.summary: Specifies that gamma correction is applied.

member.name: CompositingQuality.CompositingQualityAssumeLinear
member.summary: Specifies that gamma correction is not applied.
